      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-row"><span class="card-label">Legend</span><span class="card-value">Karttikeya's departure & Shiva-Parvati's vigil</span></div>
        <div class="card-row"><span class="card-label">River</span><span class="card-value">Krishna</span></div>
        <div class="card-row"><span class="card-label">Significance</span><span class="card-value">Both Jyotirlinga & Shakti Peetha</span></div>
