      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-row"><span class="card-label">Legend</span><span class="card-value">Ravana's devotion & Shiva's healing</span></div>
        <div class="card-row"><span class="card-label">Special</span><span class="card-value">Shravan Mela — largest annual gathering</span></div>
